signed during Narayanan's stay, the visit is putting new dynamism
into bilateral relations, which have been experiencing a full-
blown development over the past two years.
</P>
<P>
France and India established a regular system of "strategic
dialogue" two years ago and a permanent forum on bilateral
cooperation in all fields, which has already conducted four
meetings.
</P>
<P>
Trade between France and India now stands at 2 billion U.S.
dollars a year, which is relatively small considering the
potential of the two countries, said French officials.
</P>
<P>
The French aeronautics companies Aerospatiale-Matra and Airbus
Industrie hope to sell airplanes to India's national carrier, Air
India.
</P>
<P>
For this reason, France will invite Narayanan to visit the
companies' production base in Toulouse on Wednesday. 
