public service to Internet, reported the Guardian, a leading
newspaper in Nigeria, on Monday.
</P>
<P>
The paper quoted State Governor Bola Tinubu as saying that the
move will make the state, which is the economic hub of the West
African nation, more efficient in managing its natural, financial
and human resources.
</P>
<P>
