<DOCNO> XIE20000417.0326 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-17 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> More Hydropower Stations to be Built Along Yellow River </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
XINING, April 17 (Xinhua) -- China plans to build 25 major
hydropower stations in the upper reaches of the Yellow River in
the next five years, according to a government source here.
</P>
<P>
The 25 large and medium-sized power stations, the country's
largest staircase power station group when completed, will be
built along the 918 kilometers of the river. Up to ten billion
kilowatt/hour of electricity will be generated to ease the power
shortage in the east and central Chinese provinces.
</P>
<P>
With abundant water resources and great drops, the upper
reaches of the Yellow River is known as an ideal place for
hydropower development. By now, seven major hydropower stations
such as Lijiaxia, Liujiaxia and Qingtongxia, have been built with
the combined installed capacity of 5.61 million kilowatt/hour.
</P>
<P>
However, only 35.3 percent of the hydropower resources have
been utilized in the region. Some 20 sites are waiting for
exploitation in the upper reaches of the river.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE20000417.0327 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-17 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Ningxia Simplifies Exit-Entry Procedures </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YINCHUAN, April 17 (Xinhua) -- The Public Security Department
of the Ningxia Hui Autonomous Region in northwest China has
recently issued new regulations to simplify the exit-entry
procedures.
</P>
<P>
The move is part of Ningxia's response to the country's policy
to step up development of western area to narrow the gap between
prosperous eastern China and less developed western China.
</P>
<P>
In accordance with the regulations, foreign experts and
businessmen holding "L" visas can extend their stay in Ningxia
from previous one month to two months, or even three months under
special circumstances.
</P>
<P>
Besides, all eligible citizens in Ningxia can apply for private
passports only if they have a bank certificate proving that they
have a deposit of 4,000 U.S. dollars. For those who want to travel
overseas on business, they only need to submit an invitation
letter from overseas.
</P>
<P>
The time to go through necessary procedures for applying for
passports has been reduced to no more than 15 days.
</P>
<P>
Landlocked Ningxia is one of the 11 less developed areas in
western China. It is home to 18 million Hui Muslims. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
